microfilm and hard copy transmission from document retrieval centers ..AG. F. STAFFORD
an all purpose communication system is described which has theability to transmit documents both in hard copy format and inmicrofilms .  microfilms can be produced by high speed directreadout from a computer with a scan converter  and facsimilerecorder .  the facsimile printout may be graphic or alphanumeric .all communication methods, including voice communication may bechanneled into the system .